<div class="badge warning-badge">🔐 Security Alert</div>

<h1 class="title">Password Changed Successfully</h1>
<p class="subtitle">Your password has been changed successfully. Your account security has been updated.</p>

<div class="feature-list">
  <h3>Change Details</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Changed:</strong> {{changedAt}}</li>
    <li><strong>IP Address:</strong> {{ipAddress}}</li>
    <li><strong>Device:</strong> {{userAgent}}</li>
  </ul>
</div>

<div class="security-info">
  <strong>Security Notice:</strong> If you didn't make this change, please contact our support team immediately at support@deployio.tech and secure your account.
</div>

{{#if securityUrl}}
{{> button url=securityUrl label="Review Security Settings"}}
{{/if}}

<p style="color: #737373; margin: 24px 0 0 0; font-size: 14px; text-align: center;">
  <a href="mailto:support@deployio.tech" class="text-link">Contact Support</a> • 
  <a href="https://deployio.tech/security" class="text-link">Security Best Practices</a>
</p>
